value: 3443 - Fabricated Plate Work (Boiler Shops) Summary > MANCHESTER TANK & EQUIPMENT PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover fabricated plate work (boiler shops). The company is involved in the import and export of goods. MANCHESTER TANK & EQUIPMENT PTY LTD is headquartered in Echuca, Victoria. It is headed by director & general manager Kenneth Gordon Woods. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $34.18 million. Its net profit totalled $2.19 million. MANCHESTER TANK & EQUIPMENT PTY LTD forms part of the manufacturing industry sector. Key Personnel > No key personnel were found for the selected company.
